sourcesContent:
let cityData =  [
    {"id": "#modal-01",
    "modalId": "modal-01",
    "city": "Qingdao",
    "country": "China",
    "description": "Qingdao is a major seaport, naval base, and industrial centre. The world's longest sea bridge, the Jiaozhou Bay Bridge, links the main urban area of Qingdao with Huangdao district, straddling the Jiaozhou Bay sea areas. It is also the site of the Tsingtao Brewery, the second largest brewery in China.",
    "photoS": "images/portfolio/beer.jpg",
    "photo": "https://lipis.github.io/flag-icon-css/flags/4x3/cn.svg"},
    
    {"id": "#modal-02",
    "modalId": "modal-02",
    "city": "Vancouver",
   "country": "Canada",
    "description": "Vancouver is consistently named as one of the top five worldwide cities for livability and quality of life, and the Economist Intelligence Unit acknowledged it as the first city ranked among the top-ten of the world's most well-living cities for five consecutive years.",
    "photoS": "images/portfolio/coffee.jpg",
    "photo": "https://lipis.github.io/flag-icon-css/flags/4x3/ca.svg"},

    {"id": "#modal-03",
    "modalId": "modal-03",
    "city": "Boston",
    "country": "USA",
    "description": "Boston is one of the oldest municipalities in the United States, founded on the Shawmut Peninsula in 1630 by Puritan settlers from England. It was the scene of several key events of the American Revolution, such as the Boston Massacre, the Boston Tea Party, the Battle of Bunker Hill, and the Siege of Boston.",
    "photoS": "images/portfolio/farmerboy.jpg",
    "photo": "https://lipis.github.io/flag-icon-css/flags/4x3/us.svg"},

    {"id": "#modal-04",
    "modalId": "modal-04",
    "city": "Singapore",
    "country": "Singapore",
    "description": "The Republic of Singapore is an island country and city-state at the southern end of the Malay Peninsula in Asia. About 5.40 million people live in Singapore, of which 3.31 million are citizens. In Sanskrit, an old Indian language, 'Singaporean', from which Singapore got its name, means Lion City commonly ruled by Sultans.",
    "photoS": "images/portfolio/judah.jpg",
    "photo": "https://lipis.github.io/flag-icon-css/flags/4x3/sg.svg"}
   ]

export default cityData
